 Tako, i tu sam ja baš ono,

1455
00:39:21,160 --> 00:39:23,640
 rekao, Lindi, ono, stvarno,

1456
00:39:23,640 --> 00:39:24,680
 baka, ono, kao,

1457
00:39:24,680 --> 00:39:26,900
 ono što ja pričam o Viktoru Franklu

1458
00:39:26,900 --> 00:39:28,660
 i logoterapiji i smislu života,

1459
00:39:28,660 --> 00:39:30,560
 to je baka živjela, ono, stvarno.

1460
00:39:30,560 --> 00:39:32,600
 I onda nejako to sve,

1461
00:39:32,600 --> 00:39:34,320
 kao što je Frankl napisao knjigu

1462
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:35,960
 prije logora, pa su mu je uzeli,

1463
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:37,580
 pa je on to što je promišljao,

1464
00:39:37,580 --> 00:39:38,660
 doživio tamo u logore,

1465
00:39:38,660 --> 00:39:40,100
 vidio da šljaka

1466
00:39:40,100 --> 00:39:42,040
 i kasnije pisao razne knjige

1467
00:39:42,040 --> 00:39:43,780
 i tako sve, temenim tog iskustva,

1468
00:39:43,780 --> 00:39:45,120
 tako sam ja isto na životu

1469
00:39:45,120 --> 00:39:47,520
 bake i našem životu vidio da

1470
00:39:47,520 --> 00:39:49,320
 kad imaš smisao,

1471
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:51,460
 onda manje, više, ništa nije problem.

1472
00:39:51,460 --> 00:39:54,840
 Ajde, kad si već spomenuo smisao,

1473
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:55,800
 prebacit ću na knjigu,

1474
00:39:55,800 --> 00:39:57,360
 iako smo to planirati za kraj,

1475
00:39:57,360 --> 00:39:59,780
 jer umijeći sreće zapravo govori

1476
00:39:59,780 --> 00:40:00,900
 o smislu života,

1477
00:40:00,900 --> 00:40:03,400
 naša nekakva potraga uvijek za srećom

1478
00:40:03,400 --> 00:40:05,480
 se i pronalazi u smislu.

1479
00:40:05,480 --> 00:40:07,640
 Da, pa knjiga je tako nastala

1480
00:40:07,640 --> 00:40:08,820
 nakon tamo korone,

1481
00:40:08,820 --> 00:40:10,800
 kad sam ja na Whatsapp statusima pisao

1482
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:12,740
 neke kao kratke crtice ljudima

1483
00:40:12,740 --> 00:40:13,480
 za ohrabrenje,

1484
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:15,040
 prvenstveno i sebi,

1485
00:40:15,040 --> 00:40:16,500
 znači, to je više bilo

1486
00:40:16,500 --> 00:40:17,860
 ispočetka pisano kao meni,

1487
00:40:17,860 --> 00:40:18,840
 kao neko ohrabrenje,

1488
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:20,280
 u tom vremenu,

1489
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:21,700
 turbulentnom,

1490
00:40:21,700 --> 00:40:22,940
 i onda su i svi drugi,

1491
00:40:22,940 --> 00:40:24,420
 jel, i onda obično bi ja

1492
00:40:24,420 --> 00:40:27,240
 neku slikicu na kojoj pisao

1493
00:40:27,240 --> 00:40:28,960
 neki citat ili neka mudra misla,

1494
00:40:28,960 --> 00:40:30,120
 ja bi to onda,

1495
00:40:30,120 --> 00:40:31,360
 kako ti Whatsapp dopušta

1496
00:40:31,360 --> 00:40:32,300
 nekih pet rečenica,

1497
00:40:32,300 --> 00:40:33,840
 ja bi to raspisivao,

1498
00:40:33,840 --> 00:40:35,920
 da ljudi vide to neki citat,

1499
00:40:35,920 --> 00:40:37,040
 i onda stisnu pa vide

1500
00:40:37,040 --> 00:40:38,500
 ono moj tekst, jel.

1501
00:40:38,500 --> 00:40:39,960
 I tako je zapravo,

1502
00:40:39,960 --> 00:40:40,840
 ja sam počeo,

1503
00:40:40,840 --> 00:40:42,120
 i onda imao sam tu i tamo

1504
00:40:44,280 --> 00:40:46,420
 super, de nastavi još malo,

1505
00:40:46,420 --> 00:40:47,480
 taman je to bilo kako ljudi,

1506
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:48,680
 ja sam to prije posla pisao,

1507
00:40:48,680 --> 00:40:49,760
 i onda kad ljudi idu na posao

1508
00:40:49,760 --> 00:40:51,100
 da vide neku mudru misla,

1509
00:40:51,100 --> 00:40:52,420
 prije posla.

1510
00:40:52,420 --> 00:40:54,280
 I onda tamo negdje,

1511
00:40:54,280 --> 00:40:55,420
 ne znam više oko koje lekcije,

1512
00:40:55,420 --> 00:40:56,320
 preko dvijesto i neke,

1513
00:40:56,320 --> 00:40:57,400
 sam pomislio,

1514
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:58,280
 više možda bi to mogla biti

1515
00:40:58,280 --> 00:40:58,820
 knjiga kao.

1516
00:40:58,820 --> 00:41:00,180
 I onda sam to,

1517
00:41:00,180 --> 00:41:00,840
 dobro trebalo mi,

1518
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:02,080
 onda kad sam to pisao

1519
00:41:02,080 --> 00:41:02,680
 godinu dana,

1520
00:41:02,680 --> 00:41:04,020
 pa sve imao pola godine pauze,

1521
00:41:04,020 --> 00:41:05,120
 jedna mi je trebalo još godinu pol

1522
00:41:05,120 --> 00:41:06,340
 da to stvarno postane knjiga,

1523
00:41:07,120 --> 00:41:08,340
 da ima neke u glavu i repi,

1524
00:41:08,340 --> 00:41:09,500
 da se može pronaći smisa

1525
00:41:09,500 --> 00:41:10,100
 u svemu tome.

1526
00:41:10,100 --> 00:41:11,760
 I zapravo,

1527
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:12,640
 kako su umeđu vremom,

1528
00:41:12,640 --> 00:41:13,920
 su i dolazila i djeca,

1529
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:16,180
 i vidio sam da nema vremena

1530
00:41:16,180 --> 00:41:17,600
 da baviti se individualnom psihoterapijom,

1531
00:41:17,600 --> 00:41:19,300
 ali sam htio na neki način

1532
00:41:19,300 --> 00:41:20,180
 ljudima pomoći,

1533
00:41:20,180 --> 00:41:21,240
 jer vjerujem da moja knjiga,

1534
00:41:21,240 --> 00:41:22,500
 koja se čita svaki dan,

1535
00:41:22,500 --> 00:41:23,240
 jedna lekcija,

1536
00:41:23,240 --> 00:41:25,740
 i to jedna lekcija je jedna stranica,

1537
00:41:25,740 --> 00:41:26,940
 da će,

1538
00:41:26,940 --> 00:41:27,720
 da u godinu dana

1539
00:41:27,720 --> 00:41:28,940
 tog čitanja mora doći

1540
00:41:28,940 --> 00:41:29,860
 do neke osobne promjene.

1541
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:31,100
 Znači, da će to biti

1542
00:41:31,100 --> 00:41:33,360
 kao neki moj psihoterapijski učbenik,

1543
00:41:33,360 --> 00:41:35,360
 koji nije zamjena za psihoterapiju,

1544
00:41:35,360 --> 00:41:36,320
 ali ljudima,

1545
00:41:36,320 --> 00:41:37,360
 tako kroz neka pitanja

1546
00:41:37,360 --> 00:41:38,080
 koja postavljam

1547
00:41:38,080 --> 00:41:39,420
 i taj neki kraći tekst

1548
00:41:39,420 --> 00:41:40,040
 koji pročitaju,

1549
00:41:40,040 --> 00:41:41,300
 da dolazi,

1550
00:41:41,300 --> 00:41:42,620
 htio ne htio dolazi

1551
00:41:42,620 --> 00:41:43,400
 do neke promjene

1552
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:44,360
 na nekoj osobnoj razini.

1553
00:41:44,360 --> 00:41:45,000
 Tako da...

1554
00:41:45,000 --> 00:41:46,700
 Pa to stvarno ima smisla.

1555
00:41:46,700 --> 00:41:47,580
 Jer kad ti odvojiš

1556
00:41:47,580 --> 00:41:48,660
 smislenog vremena,

1557
00:41:48,660 --> 00:41:50,140
 pa makar to bilo pet minuta,

1558
00:41:50,140 --> 00:41:52,280
 jer u ovoj gunguli života

1559
00:41:52,280 --> 00:41:53,860
 nekad stvarno nemaš više,

1560
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:55,400
 ali pet minuta promisli o sebe

1561
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:56,340
 o svom životu

1562
00:41:56,340 --> 00:41:57,800
 i o odnosima koje imaš,

1563
00:41:57,800 --> 00:41:59,580
 mislim da stvarno može napraviti promjenu

1564
00:41:59,580 --> 00:42:00,700
 kad je to trajno.

1565
00:42:00,700 --> 00:42:02,040
 Svakodnevno.

1566
00:42:02,040 --> 00:42:03,140
 Ja vlam se jedna kolegica

1567
00:42:03,140 --> 00:42:05,460
 isto iz jedne psihoterapijske ustanove,

1568
00:42:05,460 --> 00:42:07,100
 oni imaju kao biblioterapiju

1569
00:42:07,100 --> 00:42:09,340
 i onda me zvala i kao

1570
00:42:09,340 --> 00:42:10,440
 jel ti znaš da tvoja knjiga

1571
00:42:10,440 --> 00:42:11,320
 kao se tu čita

1572
00:42:11,320 --> 00:42:12,140
 i ja rekao, ne znam,

1573
00:42:12,140 --> 00:42:13,060
 znam da ljudi naručuju

1574
00:42:13,060 --> 00:42:14,400
 sad ne piše niko za koje potrebe,

1575
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:14,600
 ono,

1576
00:42:14,600 --> 00:42:16,200
 i kažu da kao

1577
00:42:16,200 --> 00:42:17,280
 tvoja ime knjiga najdraža

1578
00:42:17,280 --> 00:42:18,240
 jer je kao kratka,

1579
00:42:23,960 --> 00:42:25,460
 i kao da je super

1580
00:42:25,460 --> 00:42:26,940
 i mislim ja nisam znao

1581
00:42:26,940 --> 00:42:28,060
 gdje će se sve knjiga čitati

1582
00:42:28,060 --> 00:42:28,860
 i ko će je čitati,

1583
00:42:28,860 --> 00:42:30,520
 ali stvarno je ono

1584
00:42:30,520 --> 00:42:31,480
 široko pojasno.

1585
00:42:31,480 --> 00:42:32,360
 Ja bih rekao da

1586
00:42:32,360 --> 00:42:34,800
 čak i ljudi koji nisu religiozni,

1587
00:42:34,800 --> 00:42:36,880
 knjiga je malkice religiozno pisana

1588
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:39,040
 i ja sam osoba koji je religiozno

1589
00:42:39,040 --> 00:42:39,860
 i pokušao samo napraviti

1590
00:42:39,860 --> 00:42:40,420
 da to bude,

1591
00:42:40,420 --> 00:42:41,700
 da je mogu čitati

1592
00:42:41,700 --> 00:42:43,800
 sve narodi i narodnosti

1593
00:42:43,800 --> 00:42:44,860
 što bih rekli ljudi prije,

1594
00:42:44,860 --> 00:42:46,920
 a vjerujem da sam uspio

1595
00:42:46,920 --> 00:42:48,920
 jer javljaju mi se razno razni ljudi

1596
00:42:48,920 --> 00:42:51,580
 iz Balkana cijeloga

1597
00:42:51,580 --> 00:42:52,780
 i Evrope,

1598
00:42:53,060 --> 00:42:54,400
 mislim to su makom naši ljudi

1599
00:42:54,400 --> 00:42:55,580
 u inozemstvo i tako dalje,

1600
00:42:55,580 --> 00:42:56,920
 ali stvarno je ovoga

1601
00:42:56,920 --> 00:42:58,800
 jako velika potraža za knjigom

1602
00:42:58,800 --> 00:42:59,800
 i onda stalno otiskamo

1603
00:42:59,800 --> 00:43:00,400
 nova izdanja,

1604
00:43:00,400 --> 00:43:01,340
 sad će ići peto,

1605
00:43:01,340 --> 00:43:03,280
 iće posebno zlatno izdanje,

1606
00:43:03,280 --> 00:43:04,120
 tvrde korice,

1607
00:43:04,120 --> 00:43:04,700
 ono.

1608
00:43:04,700 --> 00:43:06,400
 Super, ajde, čestitam,

1609
00:43:06,400 --> 00:43:07,000
 drago mi je.

1610
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:09,400
 Religiozno si kažeš,

1611
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:11,940
 Boga si unio ju

1612
00:43:11,940 --> 00:43:13,640
 u svoj psihoterapijski

1613
00:43:13,640 --> 00:43:15,320
 slaš knjuževni rad,

1614
00:43:15,320 --> 00:43:17,000
 a svakako je dio tvoga,

1615
00:43:17,000 --> 00:43:18,140
 svakodnevnog života.

1616
00:43:18,140 --> 00:43:19,640
 Jutro ste obilozili crkve

1617
00:43:19,640 --> 00:43:20,900
 po Mostaru, je li tako?

1618
00:43:20,980 --> 00:43:21,560
 Pa jesmo, da.

1619
00:43:21,560 --> 00:43:24,540
 Što još znači živjeti vjeru danas?

1620
00:43:24,540 --> 00:43:27,300
 Pa ja bih rekao da

1621
00:43:27,300 --> 00:43:30,420
 danas je teško biti vjernik,

1622
00:43:30,420 --> 00:43:32,040
 ono, vjernik u smislu

1623
00:43:32,040 --> 00:43:33,020
 autentičnog vjernika

1624
00:43:33,020 --> 00:43:34,720
 koji živi svakodnevni,

1625
00:43:34,720 --> 00:43:35,280
 ono, zbogom,

1626
00:43:35,280 --> 00:43:36,200
 bez neke zajednice.

1627
00:43:36,320 --> 00:43:38,860
 Smatram da živjeti s braćom u zajednici

1628
00:43:38,860 --> 00:43:40,920
 je meni pomoglo da vidiš

1629
00:43:40,920 --> 00:43:41,760
 zapravo ko si ti,

1630
00:43:41,760 --> 00:43:42,580
 kakav jesi,

1631
00:43:42,580 --> 00:43:44,420
 jer su braća često iskrena prema tebi

1632
00:43:44,420 --> 00:43:47,960
 i kroz taj hod,

1633
00:43:47,960 --> 00:43:48,960
 hod kroz zajednicu

1634
00:43:48,960 --> 00:43:50,980
 i prolaske razno raznih tema

1635
00:43:50,980 --> 00:43:53,520
 i drugih događaja u zajednici

1636
00:43:53,520 --> 00:43:55,180
 osoba produbljuje svoj odnos s Bogom.

1637
00:43:55,180 --> 00:43:56,600
 Mislim da to kao ja kao osoba

1638
00:43:56,600 --> 00:43:57,560
 ne bi nikad sam uspio.

1639
00:43:57,960 --> 00:43:58,980
 Neko možda hoće.

1640
00:43:58,980 --> 00:44:01,600
 Ja ne kažem da zajednica koja ja jesam

1641
00:44:01,600 --> 00:44:02,600
 je najbolje najispravnija.

1642
00:44:02,600 --> 00:44:02,780
 Ne.

1643
00:44:02,780 --> 00:44:04,140
 Ali Ivan Pavel II.

1644
00:44:04,140 --> 00:44:06,140
 kad je usvajao naše statute

1645
00:44:06,140 --> 00:44:06,900
 je rekao da je to

1646
00:44:06,900 --> 00:44:09,280
 ispravan put krećanske inicijacije u vjeru.

1647
00:44:09,280 --> 00:44:12,140
 Jedan od ispravnih putova.

1648
00:44:12,140 --> 00:44:13,680
 Tako da ja sam se pronašao u tome

1649
00:44:13,680 --> 00:44:14,680
 i vidim da mi to pomaže.

1650
00:44:14,680 --> 00:44:16,020
 I kad sam bio u nekim životnim

1651
00:44:16,020 --> 00:44:18,600
 najvećim tim krizama i dubiozama,

1652
00:44:18,600 --> 00:44:20,840
 psihologija mi je bila okej,

1653
00:44:20,840 --> 00:44:22,580
 ali mi je zajednica najviše pomogla.

1654
00:44:22,580 --> 00:44:23,800
 To da sam bio iskreno u zajednici

1655
00:44:23,800 --> 00:44:26,080
 i iskreno pričao o problemima

1656
00:44:26,080 --> 00:44:26,920
 koje mi se događaju.

1657
00:44:26,920 --> 00:44:28,340
 Onda meni često ljudi kažu

1658
00:44:28,340 --> 00:44:29,700
 da njema zajednica zvuči

1659
00:44:29,700 --> 00:44:30,640
 kao grupna terapija.

1660
00:44:30,640 --> 00:44:32,560
 Što donekle i je.

1661
00:44:32,560 --> 00:44:33,720
 Zapravo.

1662
00:44:33,720 --> 00:44:35,520
 Kad se mi kao braća u zajednici nađemo

1663
00:44:35,520 --> 00:44:36,540
 neka je tema,

1664
00:44:36,540 --> 00:44:38,360
 ti daješ neko svoje iskustvo.

1665
00:44:38,360 --> 00:44:40,560
 Osobno način nije da ti drugima

1666
00:44:40,560 --> 00:44:41,240
 nešto pametuješ.

1667
00:44:41,240 --> 00:44:42,720
 Ali opet to je tako kao

1668
00:44:42,720 --> 00:44:44,440
 u grupnoj terapiji

1669
00:44:44,440 --> 00:44:45,520
 ti govoriš iz ja,

1670
00:44:45,520 --> 00:44:46,880
 ono ovdje i sada

1671
00:44:46,880 --> 00:44:49,500
 i mi nemamo voditelja

1672
00:44:49,500 --> 00:44:50,500
 koji bude svećenik s nama,

1673
00:44:50,500 --> 00:44:50,900
 naravno,

1674
00:44:50,900 --> 00:44:52,320
 subotom ne koristi i tako dalje.

1675
00:44:52,920 --> 00:44:53,200
 I onda,

1676
00:44:53,200 --> 00:44:55,320
 ali kažem opet ti

1677
00:44:55,320 --> 00:44:57,560
 ti razvijaš svoj odnos sa Bogom

1678
00:44:57,560 --> 00:44:59,220
 hodajući u zajednici.

1679
00:44:59,220 --> 00:45:00,100
 Tako da ja, kažem,

1680
00:45:00,100 --> 00:45:01,420
 meni ona neprocijenjivo blago

1681
00:45:01,420 --> 00:45:05,100
 jer ne bi sigurno bio ovako hrabar

1682
00:45:05,100 --> 00:45:06,140
 i imao više djece.

1683
00:45:06,140 --> 00:45:07,180
 Možda se ne bi ni ženio.

1684
00:45:07,180 --> 00:45:08,580
 Da nisam u zajednici,

1685
00:45:08,580 --> 00:45:09,340
 da nisam vidio te ljude

1686
00:45:09,340 --> 00:45:10,120
 koji imaju više djece,

1687
00:45:10,120 --> 00:45:11,600
 da se može živjeti s više djece,

1688
00:45:11,600 --> 00:45:12,380
 da Bog proviđa.

1689
00:45:12,380 --> 00:45:13,960
 I mislim da danas ljudima

1690
00:45:13,960 --> 00:45:15,800
 fali po meni

1691
00:45:15,800 --> 00:45:17,460
 to da vjeru da Bog proviđa.

1692
00:45:17,460 --> 00:45:19,040
 Ja vjerujem da bi puno više ljudi

1693
00:45:19,040 --> 00:45:19,920
 imalo više djece

1694
00:45:19,920 --> 00:45:21,780
 kad bi znali da,

1695
00:45:21,780 --> 00:45:23,360
 jer to je ono skoku vjeri

1696
00:45:23,360 --> 00:45:25,620
 da ti prvo ti imaš šestero djece,

1697
00:45:25,620 --> 00:45:27,100
 a onda Bog pošalje minibus.

1698
00:45:27,100 --> 00:45:29,140
 Niko neće kupiti minibus

1699
00:45:29,140 --> 00:45:29,900
 sa jednim djetetom.

1700
00:45:29,900 --> 00:45:30,940
 A što znači još

1701
00:45:30,940 --> 00:45:32,180
 sljedočiti vjeru danas?

